author: Inside Edition
description: They are two of the longest unsolved crimes in American history. The Zodiac Killer was linked to five murders in the late 1960s; the 1947 Black Dahlia case centered around the killing of Elizabeth Short, a young Hollywood hopeful.
title: Did The Same Killer Commit Zodiac And Black Dahlia Crimes? #shorts

author: Inside Edition
description: The bear who moved into the crawlspace under a house seems to have found his forever home in Altadena.
title: Giant Bear Camped Out Under California Home #shorts

author: Inside Edition
description: After six surgeries and chemotherapy, Amy Berry is cancer-free. But the 53-year-old mom longs for her pre-cancer hair. "It all fell out, and it was super emotional," she told Inside Edition. She turned to hair stylist Deborah McDowell, who founded Hair With A Cause. McDowell developed hair extensions for cancer patients that will attach to just an inch of new hair growth. The process is time-consuming, taking between 14 and 16 hours.
title: Cancer Survivor Has Hair 'Magically' Restored

author: Inside Edition
description: Showing off a decadent pink layer cake, a mom wanted to try something bold. She readied herself to flip the cake in the air, and catch it rightside up. Prepping for the challenge, her kids gave her some encouragement. After a few false starts, she tried it. She's not the only one doing it, it turns out; all over social media, dessert daredevils are attempting the "Cake Flip Challenge" for themselves.
title: What Is The 'Cake Flip Challenge?'

author: Inside Edition
description: These weddings had unforgettable first dances. In 2016, newlyweds had their first dance in the middle of a traffic jam on I35 in Dayton, Ohio. In 2025, Edward LaRue and Marlene Parsons had their first dance in a pool at the YMCA, where they met. In 2016, a couple got married on the Staten Island Ferry, in front of 100 wedding guests. Afterward, their first dance was on the subway. Inside Edition Digital's Andrea Swindall has more.
title: Weddings With Unforgettable First Dances
